Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:07.22,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N14
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.11,0:00:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近校內的風紀變得有些亂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.66,0:00:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望擔任學生輔導的櫻井老師能更加嚴格地監管
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.69,0:00:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.64,0:00:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.12,0:01:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我正是為了改變自己才來擔任學生輔導老師的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須好好地監管！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼情況  這突然出現的是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不行  我絕不能就這樣退縮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.85,0:02:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何貴幹  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  那什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊走邊吃是不是稍微有失禮節…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.17,0:02:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈  失敬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我沒有吃早飯  所以肚子就突然嘶鳴起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就撤掉  失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思  沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你能理解就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  只要和他好好說還是懂的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我傳達下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常美味！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味你個頭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在走廊上發出這麼大的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微考慮一下學校風紀行不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.98,0:03:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個  把那個帶來學校的有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美里  要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笹原  午休的時候我有點話要對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖給我待在教室裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實  風紀是有點變亂了的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敬  立花美裡她是沒有惡意的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您原諒她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼  你脖子前那輕飄飄的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  感覺有點可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在日常生活中度過的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上也許是連續發生的奇跡也說不定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:04:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  就是那種東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個  那輕飄飄的到底是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗  哈哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞎扯什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼女士  有機會的話我們課堂上見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.77,0:04:49.88,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,300)\fad(600,600)\bord15\shad0\be100\3c&HFFFFFF&}學\N生\N輔\N導
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交換著看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好像很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  打擾一下  中之條同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  有什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校留這種髮型是不是稍微有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  只是有點  只是有點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  要是沒聽清我再重複一遍…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩邊的…兩邊的長不出來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:29.87,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,350)\fad(600,600)\bord15\shad0\be100\3c&HFFFFFF&}圍\N棋\N足\N球\N部\N1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:30.28,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}日本小孩玩扮鬼遊戲時念的咒語「ダルマさんが転んだ」  相當於一二三木頭人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不倒翁它…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跌倒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.59,0:05:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:40.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}請再往前一千步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:45.62,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,300)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N15
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是青梅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在家裡做梅干試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.43,0:05:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅幹…鹹死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅子對身體有益處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:06:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且加在飯團裡  飯不容易壞掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀！  名乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士我還什麼都沒說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是買了一大堆點心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先把那些好好吃完  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完了之後再來買
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以喲  今天已經和黑貓先生…叫什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  約好了買阪本先生的食物回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點心的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  請問您有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個  這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是雪人  今天上架的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您喜歡的話  請購買
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點心？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看起來像是刨冰的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要買嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  我…我只是看一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那不是雪人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說這位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:18.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個如果不買的話就給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我買
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  名乃明明就可以買自己想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士就要的就說「不行」！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不   因為這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃可以買自己想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士想買的東西也能買！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要  我想要  我就要嘛我就要！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}我知道了  就只買一個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡名乃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就買了這種東西回來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  很可愛  而且冰冰涼的感覺也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.31,0:08:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  盛好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.27,0:08:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  再給我點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你們這幫傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我的飯在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:38.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}又是5-7-5的俳句格式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這頓飯是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又冰又涼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨口說說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後出布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許亂出喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭剪刀布！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認輸…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發條！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
